{"article_id":"zAyOyXbocQiQUtNf","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Lynette Lederman says","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"she does not want the president to visit Pittsburgh","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"and will rely on local political leadership","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"A former president of the synagogue in Pittsburgh","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"where 11 people were murdered on Saturday","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"has said","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"Donald Trump would not be welcome in the city","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"and labelled the president a \" purveyor of hate speech \" .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"'Stop the words of hate , '","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"Pittsburgh rabbi urges US leaders","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"as survivors speak","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"Read more","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"Lynette Lederman , of the Tree of Life Synagogue in Squirrel Hill , told CNN on Monday","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"she would rely on local political leadership in the aftermath of the mass shooting","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"and did not want the president to visit the city .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"\" We have people","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"who stand by us ,","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"who believe in values","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"- not just Jewish -","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"but believe in values ,","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"and those are not the values of this president","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"and I do not welcome him to Pittsburgh , \"","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"she said .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"The comments followed an open letter","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"signed by a coalition of local Jewish leaders","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"and published by the Pittsburgh chapter of Bend The Arc , a progressive advocacy group ,","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"that also called for the president to avoid the city .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"\" President Trump , you are not welcome in Pittsburgh","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"until you fully denounce white nationalism , \"","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"the letter states .","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"Trump ,","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"who labelled the shooting an \" evil antisemitic attack \" ,","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"is set to visit Pittsburgh on Tuesday ,","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"the White House confirmed on Monday afternoon .","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"As the administration continues to face criticism over the president ' s polarizing rhetoric in the aftermath of the Pittsburgh shooting and a series of attempted bombings against prominent Democrats and critics of Trump last week ,","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"Trump used Twitter again on Monday morning","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"to label the media as \" the true Enemy of the People \" .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"\" There is great anger in our Country","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"caused in part by inaccurate , and even fraudulent , reporting of the news .","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"The Fake News Media , the true Enemy of the People , must stop the open & obvious hostility","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"& report the news accurately & fairly , \"","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"Trump tweeted ,","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"shortly after Lederman spoke to CNN .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"The 11 victims of the shooting were named as suspected gunman","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Robert Bowers was charged with 29 federal crimes ,","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"including 11 counts of murdering victims","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"exercising their religious beliefs .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"The shooter ,","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"who traded gunfire with law enforcement officers during the massacre ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"was released from hospital on Monday","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"and is expected in court later in the day .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"The victims , eight men and three women , ranged in age from 54 to 97","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"and included a husband and wife , two brothers , professors , a dentist and a physician .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"The Anti-Defamation League","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"[ ADL ]","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"the shooting was the most deadly attack against Jewish people in America","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"and came amid an increase in antisemitic attacks in the US .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"The ADL reported a 57 % rise in reported incidents of antisemitic harassment and violence in 2017 .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"\" We are seeing an environment","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"in which antisemitism has moved from the margins to the mainstream","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"as political candidates and people in public life literally repeat the rhetoric of white supremacists , \"","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Jonathan Greenblatt , ADL chief executive , told ABC News on Sunday .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"As the faith leadership in Squirrel Hill prepared funeral arrangements for those killed ,","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"the Tree of Life rabbi Jeffrey Myers told CNN on Monday","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"he would welcome the president to the city .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"\" I don ' t really foist blame upon any person , \"","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"Myers said .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"\" Hate does not know religion , race , creed political party -","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"it ' s not a political issue in any way shape or form .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"Hate does not know any of those things ,","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"it exists in all people . \"","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"Squirrel Hill :","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"mourners find 'safety in solidarity '","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"as they grieve","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"after shooting","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"Read more","depth":5},{"id":77,"text":"He added :","depth":5},{"id":78,"text":"\" The president of the United States is always welcome to come .","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"I ' m a citizen ,","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"he ' s my president .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"He ' s certainly welcome . \"","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"A number of fundraising efforts have driven financial support to the grieving community .","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"A crowdfunding campaign","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"called Muslims Unite for Pittsburgh Synagogue","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"has raised more than $ 90,000","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"while a fundraiser","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"led by a graduate student in Washington","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"had taken in nearly $ 545,000 by Monday morning .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"Three congregations were conducting Sabbath services at Tree of Life","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"when the attack began on Saturday morning .","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"The shooter is accused of tearing through the building with an AR-15 assault style rifle and three handguns ,","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"shouting antisemitic slurs .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"He also appears to have posted antisemitic rants on social media shortly before the attack .","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"According to law enforcement officials","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"speaking anonymously to the Associated Press ,","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"the suspect purchased all of his firearms legally","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"and was licensed to carry firearms .","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"The suspect ,","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"who had worked as a long-haul trucker ,","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"injured six other people ,","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"including four police officers","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"as they exchanged gunfire .","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"He had no previous criminal record ,","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"authorities said .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":209,"left":107,"right":208,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":107,"left":0,"right":106,"r